{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "086948c4-9e81-4271-abb7-6d6995a67304",
    "name": "Unopim DAM API",
    "description": "The UnoPim DAM (Digital Asset Management) API provides a comprehensive RESTful interface for managing digital assets, directories, properties, tags, comments, and linked resources. This API enables developers to integrate UnoPim's DAM capabilities into their applications.\n\n**Official Documentation**: [Postman Documenter](https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/21990056/2sA3kXE17F)\n\n---\n\n## \ud83d\udd10 Authentication\n\nAll API endpoints require **Bearer Token** authentication.\n\n**Headers Required**:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer {{token}}\nAccept: application/json\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## \ud83c\udf10 Base URL\n\n```\n{{url}}/api/v1/rest\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n## \ud83d\udcc2 API Resources\n\nThe API contains **23 endpoints** organized into **6 resource groups**:\n\n### 1\\. Assets (7 endpoints)\n\n- **GET** `/assets` - Get all assets (paginated)\n    \n- **GET** `/assets/{id}` - Get asset by ID\n    \n- **POST** `/assets` - Upload new asset\n    \n- **POST** `/assets/reupload` - Re-upload existing asset\n    \n- **PUT** `/assets/{id}` - Update asset metadata\n    \n- **DELETE** `/assets/{id}` - Delete asset\n    \n- **GET** `/assets/download/{id}` - Download asset file\n    \n\n### 2\\. Directories (5 endpoints)\n\n- **GET** `/directories` - Get all directories\n    \n- **GET** `/directories/{id}` - Get directory by ID\n    \n- **POST** `/directories` - Create new directory\n    \n- **PUT** `/directories/{id}` - Update directory\n    \n- **DELETE** `/directories/{id}` - Delete directory\n    \n\n### 3\\. Comments (3 endpoints)\n\n- **GET** `/comments/{id}` - Get comment by ID\n    \n- **POST** `/comments` - Create comment on asset\n    \n- **DELETE** `/comments/{id}` - Delete comment\n    \n\n### 4\\. Properties (4 endpoints)\n\n- **GET** `/properties/{id}` - Get property by ID\n    \n- **POST** `/properties/{asset_id}` - Create property for asset\n    \n- **PATCH** `/properties/{id}` - Update property\n    \n- **DELETE** `/properties/{id}` - Delete property\n    \n\n### 5\\. Tags (3 endpoints)\n\n- **GET** `/tags/{id}` - Get tag by ID\n    \n- **POST** `/tags` - Create and associate tag with asset\n    \n- **DELETE** `/tags` - Remove tag\n    \n\n### 6\\. Linked Resources (1 endpoint)\n\n- **GET** `/linked-resource/{id}` - Get linked resources",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "createdAt": "2026-01-16T12:16:04.000Z",
